Package org.semanticweb.owl.align

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Alignment
    Represents an Ontology alignment.
    AlignmentProcess
    Represents an executable alignment
    AlignmentRepairer
    Represents an operator for repairing alignments and networks of alignments.
    AlignmentVisitor  
    Cell
    Represents an correspondence between ontology entities.
    Evaluator
    Assess the closeness between two ontology alignments.
    LogicOntologyNetwork
    Represents a distributed system of aligned ontologies or network of ontologies.
    OntologyNetwork
    Represents a distributed system of aligned ontologies or network of ontologies.
    Parameters
    A set of parameters to be passed to an alignment or evaluation method.
    Relation  
    Visitable
    The interface of the objects that can be visited by a renderer
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AlignmentException
    Base class for all Alignment Exceptions.
